<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA68">
<l>kalluṅ kaṉaikaṭalum vaikunta vāṉāṭum</l>
<l>pulleṉ ṟaḻintaṉakol lēpāvam vella</l>
<l>neṭiyā ṉiṟaṅkariyā ṉuṭpukuntu nīṅkā</l>
<l>ṉaṭiyēṉa tuḷḷat takam.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Stone and sounding sea and the heavenly land Vaikunta,</l>
<l>have they become emptily desolate, o evil? Victoriously</l>
<l>the Tall one, the one black in colour has entered inside [and] does not leave,</l>
<l>the inside of the mind of me who am [his] servant.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
